data.description: Great duplex property fully remodeled and already tenant occupied!! Spacious units featuring upgraded wood laminate flooring and fully renovated kitchen areas, including white cabinets, backsplash, & stainless steel appliance! Nice sized bedrooms and beautifully finished bathrooms with new vanities! Fenced in yard & home is on a large corner lot!! All located near major intersections/ close to Fremont St...
